# Copy to `.dev.vars` for local `wrangler dev`. In production set with
# `wrangler secret put AUTH_KEY` (NEVER commit real values — .dev.vars is gitignored).

# A string you invent. Callers must pass it as ?key=<AUTH_KEY> (or the
# `x-auth-key` header) on POST /transcribe. If left unset, the endpoint is OPEN —
# fine for local dev, do NOT deploy without it.
AUTH_KEY=
